      "data": {
        "title": "How to set it up",
        "summary": "Use the toolbar strip first, then the save panel. `Document` tells you what graph is open, `Save target` tells you where the next write goes, and `Access` tells you which installation context Twilite is using. Missing repos are usually installation-scope issues on GitHub, not local-folder issues. The practical procedure now lives in the GitHub how-to document, while the walkthrough demonstrates the full round trip.",
